  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "I would suggest to change `_duration` to `uint32` which would still allow a vesting duration of max ~ 136 years.\r\n\r\nThis will allow the compiler to put all these values into one (instead of 2) 256 bit storage slots.\r\n\r\n```\r\n    address private immutable _beneficiary; // 160 Bit\r\n    uint64 private immutable _start;        //  64 Bit\r\n    uint32 private immutable _duration;     //  32 Bit \r\n```\r\n\r\nAlternative : change `_start` and `_duration` both to `uint48`",
